text: The Örgryte New Church () is a church building in Örgryte in the town of Gothenburg in Sweden. It belongs to the Örgryte Parish of the Church of Sweden. The church was opened on 6 July 1890. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:Churches in Gothenburg Category:Buildings and structures completed in the 19th century
title: Örgryte New Church
